OL,3,CWarning lives are at risk on Welsh
OL,4,Crailway lines as anti-social instances
OL,5,Crise
OL,7,FTransport for Wales is issuing a stark
OL,8,Fwarning that lives are being put at
OL,9,Frisk as cases of anti-social behaviour
OL,10,Fincrease on Welsh railway lines.
OL,12,FThe rail service provider says anti-
OL,13,Fsocial behaviour has risen by 28% so
OL,14,Ffar this year at stations on Core
OL,15,FValley routes, with Abercynon and
OL,16,FPorth having the highest percentage of
OL,17,Fincidents.
