OL,7,FDespite an increase in anti-social
OL,8,Fbehaviour, TfW say there has been a
OL,9,F38% fall in the number of people
OL,10,Ftrespassing on the lines so far this
OL,11,Fyear, compared with the same period in
OL,12,F2023.
OL,14,FThe types of problem behaviour being
OL,15,Freported include individuals throwing
OL,16,Fstones at trains and across the
OL,17,Ftracks, and items being dropped and
OL,18,Fcollected from the track.
