OL,5,Crise
OL,7,FShe said: "While it's encouraging to
OL,8,Fsee a declining trend in reported
OL,9,Ftrespassing incidents, the
OL,10,Fintroduction of OLE marks the need for
OL,11,Fcontinued caution.
OL,13,F"Worryingly, there seems to be more
OL,14,Fand more school-aged children
OL,15,Ftrespassing when the stakes are higher
OL,16,Fthan ever.
OL,18,F"Everyone, no matter their age, needs
OL,19,Fto be aware of the dangers. Even just
OL,20,Fone incident of trespassing could be
OL,21,Ffatal.
