OL,4,Crailway lines as anti-social instances
OL,5,Crise
OL,7,F"However, it's not just trespassing
OL,8,Fthat is unsafe. Electricity from OLE
OL,9,Fcan jump, and the risk of
OL,10,Felectrocution without direct contact
OL,11,Fis significantly higher.
OL,13,F"This means anti-social activities
OL,14,Fthat people may not have deemed as
OL,15,F'dangerous' before can now have even
OL,16,Fmore serious, potentially life-
OL,17,Fthreatening consequences.
