OL,7,FTfW says it has been taking additional
OL,8,Fmeasures to improve safety and
OL,9,Fsecurity around railway tracks, with
OL,10,Fnew fencing and extended safety
OL,11,Fbarriers being added to key areas as
OL,12,Fwell as drones monitoring for
OL,13,Fincidents of trespassing and anti-
OL,14,Fsocial behaviour.
OL,16,FBut it says the numbers of cable
OL,17,Fthefts and damage are still
OL,18,Fincreasing, showing that people are
OL,19,Fstill trespassing on the tracks
OL,20,Fdespite the added dangers.
